dataArray: Ghawr adh Dhra' Wa al Hanawah
Rawdat al Amir `Ali Bin al Husayn
Al Khanasiri al Hayy al Gharbi
Az Zubaydiyah al Hayy al Janubiyah
Mintaqat al Quwaysimah wa Abu `Alanda wa ar Rajib
Mintaqat Tila` al `Ali wa Umm as Summaq wa Khilda
Mintaqat Umm Qusayr wa al Muqabalayn wa al Bunayyat
Hayy as Safih wa al Baqi`
Hayy ath Thawrah al `Arabiyah al Kubra
Hayy Wadi ad Dayr al Gharbi
Hayy Wadi ad Dayr ash Sharqi
